      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 20,
      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "## HRIV Usage Overview\n\nAggregate usage analytics from structured logs (Loki). **No named-user panels are provisioned** — Grafana dashboard provisioning is broadly readable, so listing individual users here would expose per-person activity to everyone with dashboard access. Per-user drill-down is intentionally left to ad-hoc, access-controlled log queries. If a safe, restricted provisioning mechanism (a separate access-scoped folder/org) is later established, add named-user panels there.\n\nSynthetic-monitor journeys are excluded from every panel via the server-marked `event_synthetic` / `auth_synthetic` flag.\n\n> Field names assume OTLP→Loki ingestion, which sanitizes attribute dots to underscores (e.g. `event.name` → `event_name`). Adjust the `service` variable / label names if your Loki label pipeline differs.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.0.0",
      "title": "Privacy & scope",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${loki}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }] },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 5, "x": 0, "y": 5 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${loki}" },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service_name=\"${service}\"} | event_name=\"navigation.page_changed\" | event_synthetic!=\"true\" [$__range]))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Page hits",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${loki}" },
